M|Budg|When|
M|Budg|tx|\| Variance \| Action \|
M|Budg|tx|\|---------\|--------\|
M|Budg|tx|\| < 5% over \| Note it; monitor nx month \|
M|Budg|tx|\| 5–15% over \| Flag to dn; identify root cause \|
M|Budg|tx|\| > 15% over \| Flag to mc AND dn immediately; pause new spend until resolved \|
M|Budg|tx|\| > 20% over \| Emergency rv; propose reallocation before nx spend cycle \|
M|Budg|tx|\| Under budget by > 20% \| Check if activity was deferred — flag as risk if ct work is slipping \|
M|Budg|tx|Variance is not always bad — underspend on a key initiative is a planning fl, not a win.
